cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is about a toolkit for pre-trained word embeddings, which is a common topic in natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses evaluation and extraction of embeddings, which are related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The visualization module is also relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the paper demonstrates the effectiveness of the toolkit on a name entity recognition (NER) task, which falls under the sub-category of neural networks and deep learning (cs.NE).
